 weeks, driven a wedge of panic into the psyche of men and women across the world. May 2, 2020 In "News" The House of Representatives yesterday called on the Federal Government to ignore the World Health Organization, WHO, in efforts to find cure for COVID-19 and approve use of alternative remedies to cure the disease. May 13, 2020 In "Coronavirus Updates"